cast.overview: Resolving to achieve professional success without compromising her ethics, Lucy embarks on a ruthless game of one-upmanship against cold and efficient nemesis Joshua, a rivalry that is complicated by her growing attraction to him.
cast.title: The Hating Game

details.biography: Brock Yurich was born on May 1, 1989 in New Philadelphia, Ohio, USA as Brock Taylor Yurich. He is an actor and producer, known for T-County (2016), 49: A Tribute to Pulse Night Club (2017) and Test.
details.name: Brock Yurich
details.place_of_birth: New Philadelphia, Tuscarawas County, Ohio, USA
